item.title: Thelymitra malvina
item.dc:creator: russell
item.description: Along with previous observation (10253), this shows the limits of the positions where this new species record for Wilsons Prom was seen - about 6-10 plants seen on the side of the track. Plants were open in pouring rain (no sun).

item.title: Thelymitra malvina
item.dc:creator: russell
item.description: New species record for Wilsons Prom. Nearest records are west of Korumburra and Providence Ponds Reserve (east of Sale). Distinctive mauve tufts on column arms. Apparently opens only in mornings. These were open in pouring rain (no sun).
